  stable on x86, alpha, ia64

  22 Feb 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> vim-core-6.2-r1.ebuild,
  vim-core-6.2-r2.ebuild, vim-core-6.2-r3.ebuild, vim-core-6.2-r4.ebuild,
